@Francis Thank you!! I must admit I always enjoy reading your comments when I scroll through so I’m almost a little… starstruck! Haha. I’ll try to come back more often 🤩

 Yes that’s totally true, and a fact I love about the stars! I believe I’ve read it’s because the universe is ever expanding that the constellations will always be shifting. I wonder if in another millennium, assuming we’re still inhabiting the planet, what we’d see them as! And yet like you said, we have managed to see the same things in them over thousands of years. I really do find it an inspiring and comforting thought. 

